---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Martial Arts & TCM" description="Discover Chinese martial arts from Shaolin to Tai Chi, plus the ancient wisdom of Traditional Chinese Medicine">
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/images/tai-chi.jpg"
        alt="Chinese martial arts Tai Chi"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1a1a1a]/95 to-[#00A86B]/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="inline-block font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-[#D4AF37] mb-4">MARTIAL</span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl text-white mb-6">Martial Arts & TCM</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
          From Shaolin's thundering fists to Tai Chi's flowing grace. Plus the ancient healing wisdom of Traditional Chinese Medicine.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#FFFEF7]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-[#C41E3A] mb-4">PHILOSOPHY IN MOTION</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6">Wushu: The Art of War Refined</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600">
          Chinese martial arts (武术, wǔshù) are not merely about combat — they are a path to self-cultivation, integrating physical discipline, moral character, and spiritual development. The legendary Shaolin monks fused Buddhist meditation with fighting techniques, while internal styles like Tai Chi emphasize harmony between mind and body.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {[
          { name: 'Shaolin Kung Fu', origin: 'Henan Province', desc: 'The most famous Chinese martial art, developed by Buddhist monks at the Shaolin Temple. Known for powerful, dynamic movements and forms.', style: 'External', icon: '🏯' },
          { name: 'Tai Chi (Taijiquan)', origin: 'Chen Village', desc: 'An internal martial art emphasizing slow, flowing movements. Practiced worldwide for health, meditation, and self-defense.', style: 'Internal', icon: '☯️' },
          { name: 'Wing Chun', origin: 'Southern China', desc: 'A close-range combat style attributed to a Buddhist nun. Known for efficient, direct techniques and centerline theory.', style: 'Internal', icon: '🥋' },
          { name: 'Praying Mantis', origin: 'Shandong Province', desc: 'A striking style inspired by the insect\'s movements. Features hook punches, elbow strikes, and rapid combinations.', style: 'External', icon: '🦗' },
          { name: 'Baguazhang', origin: 'Northern China', desc: 'An internal style characterized by walking circles and palm changes. Emphasizes evasion, flexibility, and weapon use.', style: 'Internal', icon: '🔄' },
          { name: 'Xingyiquan', origin: 'Shanxi Province', desc: 'An aggressive internal style with explosive, straight-line movements. Originally designed for battlefield combat.', style: 'Internal', icon: '⚡' }
        ].map(style => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="text-4xl">{style.icon}</span>
              <span class={`px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm ${style.style === 'Internal' ? 'bg-green-100 text-green-700' : 'bg-orange-100 text-orange-700'}`}>
                {style.style}
              </span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">{style.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-[#00A86B] text-sm mb-3">{style.origin}</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">{style.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TCM Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="/images/yin-yang.jpg"
            alt="Traditional Chinese Medicine and martial arts"
            class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <span class="inline-block font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-[#D4AF37] mb-4">HEALING WISDOM</span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-white mb-6">Traditional Chinese Medicine</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-stone-400 mb-6">
            Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM) is a complete medical system that has treated patients for over 2,000 years. Based on the concept of qi (vital energy) flowing through the body, TCM takes a holistic approach to health and wellness.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              { name: 'Acupuncture', desc: 'Thin needles inserted at specific points to balance qi flow' },
              { name: 'Herbal Medicine', desc: 'Natural formulas combining plants, minerals, and animal products' },
              { name: 'Cupping Therapy', desc: 'Glass cups create suction to improve blood flow' },
              { name: 'Tui Na Massage', desc: 'Therapeutic massage along energy meridians' },
              { name: 'Moxibustion', desc: 'Burning mugwort to warm and stimulate acupuncture points' }
            ].map(tx => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-stone-800/50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#00A86B]"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-white">{tx.name}</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">{tx.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Five Elements -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#00A86B]/10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">The Five Elements (Wu Xing)</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          TCM and martial arts both draw from the ancient theory of Five Elements: Wood, Fire, Earth, Metal, and Water. These elements interact in cycles of generation and control, forming the basis of health, personality, and technique.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-4">
        {[
          { element: '木 Wood', organ: 'Liver', season: 'Spring', emotion: 'Anger', color: 'bg-green-600' },
          { element: '火 Fire', organ: 'Heart', season: 'Summer', emotion: 'Joy', color: 'bg-red-600' },
          { element: '土 Earth', organ: 'Spleen', season: 'Late Summer', emotion: 'Worry', color: 'bg-amber-600' },
          { element: '金 Metal', organ: 'Lungs', season: 'Autumn', emotion: 'Sadness', color: 'bg-stone-600' },
          { element: '水 Water', organ: 'Kidneys', season: 'Winter', emotion: 'Fear', color: 'bg-blue-600' }
        ].map(el => (
          <div class={`${el.color} rounded-xl p-6 text-white text-center`}>
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">
              {el.element === '木 Wood' ? '🌳' : el.element === '火 Fire' ? '🔥' : el.element === '土 Earth' ? '🏔️' : el.element === '金 Metal' ? '⚔️' : '💧'}
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg mb-2">{el.element}</h3>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-80">
              <div>{el.organ}</div>
              <div>{el.season}</div>
              <div>{el.emotion}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00A86B] to-[#008B57]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white mb-4">Continue Exploring</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-8">
        Discover the philosophical foundations behind these practices.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-[#00A86B] font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100 transition-colors">
          Back to Home
        </a>
        <a href="/daoism" class="px-6 py-3 border border-white text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          Explore Daoism
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
